### -------------------------------
### [POST] Izveido studiju līmeni
POST http://localhost:8080/api/study-levels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bakalaura",
  "description": "Pamatlīmenis augstākajā izglītībā"
}

###

### [POST] Izveido studiju formu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/study-forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pilna laika",
  "description": "Pilna laika klātienes studijas"
}

###

### [POST] Izveido valodu
POST http://localhost:8080/api/languages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Latviešu valoda",
  "code": "lv"
}

###

### [POST] Izveido kursa un programmas sasaisti (iegultie objekti ar ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-study-programs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": { "id": "47a251e1-e02f-49a6-b61f-40f35b69a9b4" },
  "program": { "id": "1" }
}

### ---------------------------------------------------
### [GET] Pieprasījumi visām entītijām

GET http://localhost:8080/api/study-levels
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/study-forms
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/languages
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-study-programs

### ---------------------------------------------------
### [PUT] Atjauno studiju līmeni ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/study-levels/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bakalaura līmenis",
  "description": "Atjaunināts apraksts"
}

###

### [PUT] Atjauno studiju formu ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/study-forms/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nepilna laika",
  "description": "Vakara vai brīvdienu studijas"
}

###

### [PUT] Atjauno valodu ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/languages/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Angļu valoda",
  "code": "en"
}

###

### [PUT] Atjauno sasaisti ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-study-programs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": { "id": "d791dcbe-62dc-4527-aa73-d19793a1db73" },
  "program": { "id": "2" }
}

