### [DELETE] Dzēš ierakstus pēc ID (ja nepieciešams)

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/study-levels/1
###
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/study-forms/1
###
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/languages/1
